body:
Please use the below files to recreate the issue. Use following command(copy rnn_tc.txt as rnn_tc.py first). python3 tensorflow version is 1.3.0:

$python3 rnn_tc.py

We got following messages:

$ python3 rnn_tc.py > tc.log4
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "rnn_tc.py", line 62, in <module>
    'dbpedia', size='big')
  File "/usr/local/lib/python3.4/dist-packages/tensorflow/contrib/learn/python/learn/datasets/__init__.py", line 71, in load_dataset
    return DATASETS[name](size, test_with_fake_data)
  File "/usr/local/lib/python3.4/dist-packages/tensorflow/contrib/learn/python/learn/datasets/text_datasets.py", line 65, in load_dbpedia
    train_path, target_dtype=np.int32, features_dtype=np.str, target_column=0)
  File "/usr/local/lib/python3.4/dist-packages/tensorflow/contrib/learn/python/learn/datasets/base.py", line 72, in load_csv_without_header
    data = np.array(data)
**MemoryError**


[rnn_tc.txt](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/files/1535219/rnn_tc.txt)
